ChannelKeys":null,"inputs":{"extensible":false,"data":{}},"outputs":{"extensible":false,"data":{}},"runtime":{},"display":{},"comments":{"title":"Flow Overview","markdown":"The flow takes fields passed by the parent and creates an OIDC basic application in Okta using nested object constructs. The overall structure of the flow is the same as SAML Create App. The key differences are:\n1. The app is always hidden from the Okta dashboard.\n2. Custom scopes/claims are collected if received from parent, but they are not processed via automation. The custom scopes/claims are collected into a SCTask for manual fulfillment. A future enhancement can be added to handle custom authorization servers.\n3. App metadata (such as client id/secret) is not sent back to the user during ticket closure. A SCTask is generated for fulfillment in this flow. If your organization has a secrets vault or manager, you can send a request there.\n\nThis flow shares the Group Assignment, Policy Assignment, and Comms helper flows with SAML App Create."}}},"pins":{}},{"joins":{},"address":"root:kernel:control:0.0.1:comment","parents":{"version":{"address":"root:kernel:control:0.0.1","key":"0.0.1","data":{"name":"0.0.1"}},"channel":{"address":"root:kernel:control","key":"control","data":{"name":"control"}}},"uuid":"WV0rReHxx","branches":{},"node":{"key":"comment","data":{"name":"Comment"},"model":{"type":"method","_v":2,"key":"comment","executable":false,"displayed":true,"async":false,"cooperative":false,"mirrored":false,"inlined":false,"dependencies":[],"timeout":90000,"idempotent":false,"monitor":false,"webhook":false,"webhookList":false,"webhookConditions":false,"mobile":false,"hooks":{},"policy":{"error":{"type":"finish"}},"metadata":{"id":null,"name":"Comment","description":"Leave a comment."},"meta":{},"config":null,"partnerChannelKeys":null,"inputs":{"extensible":false,"data":{}},"outputs":{"extensible":false,"data":{}},"runtime":{},"display":{},"comments":{"title":"T.E.A.M. & PKCE","markdown":